WEBVTT

00:00.242 --> 00:02.112
Previously on
<i>Falling Skies...</i>

00:02.137 --> 00:03.464
It might know
everything.

00:03.465 --> 00:04.856
And if it <i>doesn't</i> talk?

00:04.881 --> 00:07.196
How long have you been
in communication with him?

00:07.221 --> 00:08.651
Some of them
have been able to

00:08.676 --> 00:10.256
resist the effects
of the harness.

00:10.281 --> 00:11.748
So, how can I
convince you?

00:11.773 --> 00:13.880
Together, we could do what
neither of us could do alone -

00:13.905 --> 00:15.431
overthrow
our oppressors.

00:16.831 --> 00:17.663
What are you doing?!

00:17.688 --> 00:19.325
So let's stop
playing games, okay?

00:21.166 --> 00:22.496
We're not safe here.

00:22.521 --> 00:23.652
The fish-heads.

00:23.677 --> 00:25.068
They're looking for you.

00:25.093 --> 00:26.268
They're looking
for your boy -- Ben.

00:26.293 --> 00:28.293
I have to go away.

00:32.302 --> 00:33.769
Where are you taking me?

00:33.803 --> 00:36.473
There's a group of Skitters
who have developed an ability

00:36.507 --> 00:37.676
to resist their harnesses.

00:37.711 --> 00:38.880
You mean act of
their own free will?

00:38.914 --> 00:40.513
I don't know
how they did it,

00:40.547 --> 00:42.515
but they've started a rebellion
against the Overlords.

00:42.550 --> 00:44.954
How did you
find out about this?

00:44.988 --> 00:47.292
Their leader
contacted me.

00:47.326 --> 00:48.794
How?

00:48.828 --> 00:51.397
Through my spikes,
the same way connected.

00:51.431 --> 00:55.500
When I was harnessed,
I saw and heard a lot of stuff.

00:55.534 --> 00:57.635
I mean, I could tell them
all kinds of things.

00:57.669 --> 00:59.504
Battle plans,
defenses --

00:59.538 --> 01:02.241
Maybe, but we do still
have to find them.

01:02.276 --> 01:03.410
How?

01:04.780 --> 01:06.014
Skitters.

01:06.049 --> 01:07.750
Close by.
Rebels?

01:07.784 --> 01:09.520
Don't know yet.

01:15.663 --> 01:16.930
Hold it.
Those aren't --

01:16.966 --> 01:20.502
You're right, Ben.
They're not rebels.

01:22.072 --> 01:24.508
They're with us.

